## 二、自定义图标
```css
/* 字体转Base64的内容 */
@font-face {
  font-family: 'FontIcons';
  src: url('data:font/woff2;charset=utf-8;base64,xxx') format('woff');
  font-weight: normal;
  font-style: normal;
  font-display: swap;
}
.icon{font-family: 'FontIcons' !important; font-size: 16px;}
/* 对应字体图标编号 */
.icon_test{content: "\e900";}
```

- 图标生成: [https://icomoon.io/app/#/select](https://icomoon.io/app/#/select)
- 转Base64: [https://transfonter.org/](https://transfonter.org/)
